''' Chhṳ̀-san ''' (Charity, 慈善) he yit-chúng san-liòng yi-ngien ke sa-fi fa̍t-thûng, kôan-he "[[chhṳ̀-san-kâ|Sṳ̂-yi-chá]]" lâu "Su-sṳ̂-chá". Chhai [[sa-fi]] sông, put-mun vu̍t-chṳt fì po thi, pûn-yi yû sî-yeu ke sa-khiùn pông-chhu, [[chan-chhu]] tén. 
Chhṳ̀-san he chhiuk-chin [[ngìn-lui]] fuk-li chin-phu ke li-kì kôan-fài, thûng-sòng théu-ko kiên-chen kîm-chhièn, chṳ̂-sán fe̍t fa̍t-thûng, yù [[kau-yuk]] fe̍t yî-liàu kî-kèu kiên chen yi yû sî-khiù ke ngìn, fe̍t kûng yit hia̍p-chhu khì-thâ sa-fi sî-khiù. <ref>[http://db1x.Sinica.Edu.Tw/caat/caat_rptcaatc.Php?_op=?SUBJECT_ID:300253947 ngi-su̍t lâu kien-chuk sok yín tién － chhṳ̀ san] yî 2011-ngièn 3-ngie̍t 31-ngit chhà ye̍t </ref>

